				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Combat Leader: Volkssturm &#039;45 Expansion Module" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>From the publisher's web site:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is the second expansion module for the Combat Leader game system.  It introduces the German Volkssturm forces available near the end of the war.  You must own Combat Leader:  East Front '41 to use this expansion.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It includes a counter sheet (Set D) with 27 Volkssturm men, and a new 12-man Russian first line squad, as well as Map 5 (8.5&amp;quot;x11&amp;quot;), additional Reference Card, and instruction folder.  New rules cover the use of Volkssturm in scenarios, and special rules governing their use.  Also instructions governing the use of improvised weapons (such as antique rifles, shotguns, the MP 3008, and panzerfausts) are provided.  Finally, Scenario VKS-1 (Outskirts of Berlin) lets you use the new components in a situation set in Greater Berlin, May 1945.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Like the previous expansion, this one builds on the foundation provided in the core rules, and is compatible with any Combat Leader game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
